{"tid":927852,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如何 回到 當時","createTime":"2018-12-04T12:21:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T16:27:51.000Z","uid":10759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"824a8e449513113099dad1cf04f4c1fde64b931e","tid":927852,"uid":10759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T12:21:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"></span>"},{"pid":"a694cf8b3902b3b440ca38be33a867a3efbfeb24","tid":927852,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T12:23:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"></span>"},{"pid":"6d8b07c2157dea2c0968ea9b7d4d8e05cc042daa","tid":927852,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T12:25:15.000Z","msg":"<strong></strong>"},{"pid":"abb597525022de31fe6ce653f7e6961b169e9a2c","tid":927852,"uid":124256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T12:27:42.000Z","msg":"揾多啦A夢"},{"pid":"3ff2b272c97af2696742daa912ead6ba1d2ff8ed","tid":927852,"uid":111271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T12:30:58.000Z","msg":"記憶可以"},{"pid":"c73dcdcdc8c1e60717fb3618c3825242ebd3f131","tid":927852,"uid":56505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T12:43:54.000Z","msg":"時間旅行泛指人或物體由某一時間點移至另一時間點，類似在空間中的移動。所有事物都順著時間一分一秒地自然前進，因此這裡的時間旅行單指違反這種自然時間變化的方式：前往未來，或是回到過去。這在哲學（英語：Philosophy of space and time）和虛構作品（英語：Time travel in fiction）中是廣為人知的概念。時間旅行通常藉著存在於假想中的時間機器進行，這概念因1895年H&middot;G&middot;威爾斯的小說《時間機器》而普及起來。<br />\n<br />\n根據目前的物理學，無法確定是否可能進行回溯時間旅行（回到過去）；而在狹義相對論和廣義相對論的架構下，朝向未來的時間旅行已被透徹了解，且是經過大量觀測的現象。然而，現今的科技無法讓一物相對於另一物的時間超越或延遲超過幾毫秒。至於回溯的時間旅行，找到允許這件事的廣義相對論解（英語：Exact solutions in general relativity）不是不可能，但符合該解的條件可能在物理上無法達成。理論物理學對時空旅行的支持非常有限，通常只牽涉到量子力學（英語：Quantum mechanics of time travel）或蟲洞。"},{"pid":"801e408007f79905f82a89f5430fc4a0d2ca4411","tid":927852,"uid":8613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T12:54:02.000Z","msg":"柔如情侶熱戀的那時"},{"pid":"05afd77d193c6d89ec0ecc787214a30cebb886b0","tid":927852,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:37:44.000Z","msg":"長埋是你嗎 何以未講一聲 就撇下我 回答吧"},{"pid":"fea0b7e8a65c8cd7322f9199ec32a6b956d67997","tid":927852,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T14:04:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d09f8ec7ede517188cdc5ed4976544e35cb28d33","tid":927852,"uid":112390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T14:05:13.000Z","msg":"。。。"},{"pid":"afd13fdbb9501817a745cb5885d32be1a2d4d5e6","tid":927852,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T16:27:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}